  * Fix const var init with NRVO (#3803)

  [ nv-jdeligiannis ]
  * Allowing use of const static variables in library exports (#3780)

  [ Adam Yang ]
  * Fixed int16_t type name in debug info (#3804)

  [ Lukas Hermanns ]
